<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.1">
<l>tivaḷumveṇ matipōl tirumukat tarivai ceḻuṅkaṭa lamutiṉiṟ piṟanta</l>
<l>vavaḷuniṉ ṉākat tiruppatu maṟintu mākilu mācaivi ṭāḷāl</l>
<l>kuvaḷaiyaṅ kaṇṇi kolliyam pāvai colluniṉ tāḷnayan tirunta</l>
<l>vivaḷaiyuṉ maṉattā leṉṉiṉain tiruntā yiṭaventai yentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though knowing of the one who was born of nectar from the fertile sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">the lady whose divine face is like the shining, white moon,</l>
<l>Being on your chest, never the less, the lotus-eyed maid of Kolli [Hills]</l>
<l>Will clearly not leave [off] her longing. Tell [me]; in your mind,</l>
<l>What you were you intending for her who has adored your feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord father of Iṭaventai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
